re":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T23:39:41.000Z","msg":"朋友住果到<br />\n退休的話我覺得好ok<br />\n夠靜環境都幾好<br />\n但真係加唔方便"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T01:01:01.000Z","msg":"睇咩時間啦, 朝早返學嘈到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T01:51:54.000Z","msg":"原來鬼仔學校都開咪架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0fc49b8856f8135fdb172b60af30052b9c7f82","tid":1991940,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T01:55:54.000Z","msg":"有咩山係周圍都係人名架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd46b372067f790eaf7b2bd1118aa3e30ef9dbf","tid":1991940,"uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T01:57:41.000Z","msg":"以香港人normal standard根本住唔過，唔講生活必需配套先，個區真係住滿曬人塞車塞鳩死你"},{"pid":"2f4aa881d32660892eb31ce5b691a4b4ffe1f7e1","tid":1991940,"uid":234756,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:08:06.000Z","msg":"前果排都有睇滿名山，覺得尺價真係抵住，加上又無咁近市區，感覺寧靜D，又鐘意佢一房果個L型open kitchen。<br />\n<br />\n但住果度既話你預左一定唔會揸車，應該係話想揸都無得揸，住得果度就係貪佢尺價平，你仲要睇緊細單位，果度因為車位少，所以貴到仆街，好似成兩百五十萬，加上我返工唔起果邊，諗到日日來回3個鐘車程就想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除非你返工起屯門果邊，如果唔係真係要三思，寧願貴少少考慮下其他盤，唔好覺得可以好似你個名咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好少覆咁大篇野"},{"pid":"19637c0db1e039b1510b4da191b2d1660624fae3","tid":1991940,"uid":352996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:14:47.000Z","msg":"平係有原因"},{"pid":"9cddf52e15dec156a07106e7b60ebac20afaa91c","tid":1991940,"uid":274725,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:25:46.000Z","msg":"冇嘢食 得間會所餐廳又難食又貴<br />\n冇嘢買 買餸要坐交通工具<br />\n車位貴 易塞車 近屯門公路 屋苑內好撚多灰塵<br />\n屋苑內種好多樹 多蚊 落大雨會好多地方有泥水 因為有啲路段係放舊石係啲泥上面俾你行<br />\n去屯西要15-20分鐘因為多燈位 如果揸車分分鐘深井出荃灣仲快過滿名去西鐵站<br />\n會所啲職員廢 做嘢慢 成日俾人投訴 態度差<br />\n健身室望住屯門公路跑步 對到正一正<br />\n有村巴出西鐵站但要俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為近國際學校 好撚多蝗蟲係你鄰居 兩成係鬼佬呀差 三成香港人 一半係支那狗<br />\n下面係入境學院 好撚多TB出出入入 <br />\n呢個尺價真心唔抵"},{"pid":"66365e2e8b9c04f979a8f23f53a02d622b814b8e","tid":1991940,"uid":274725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"78e1a02432330cf03d3d090b358a50bc5ac67a77","tid":1991940,"uid":240276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cf686c332be685ccde3b18c7e33551479f816b6","tid":1991940,"uid":26811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b94850f8c1cca148feee31c1d6515a93307454cf","tid":1991940,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T23:39:41.000Z","msg":"朋友住果到<br />\n退休的話我覺得好ok<br />\n夠靜環境都幾好<br />\n但真係加唔方便"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T01:01:01.000Z","msg":"睇咩時間啦, 朝早返學嘈到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T01:51:54.000Z","msg":"原來鬼仔學校都開咪架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T02:29:11.000Z","msg":"你以為全部都係鬼仔呀？好撚多支那狗讀呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf1c0c79d03ded8d1c1ab00a9b15914730fbbcb","tid":1991940,"uid":119825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d0fc49b8856f8135fdb172b60af30052b9c7f82","tid":1991940,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T01:55:54.000Z","msg":"有咩山係周圍都係人名架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"咪就係,唔知點解可以作呢個名出嚟"},{"pid":"622581492d30686c11eeb006e4a213b23f8a853e","tid":1991940,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cf686c332be685ccde3b18c7e33551479f816b6","tid":1991940,"uid":26811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b94850f8c1cca148feee31c1d6515a93307454cf","tid":1991940,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T23:39:41.000Z","msg":"朋友住果到<br />\n退休的話我覺得好ok<br />\n夠靜環境都幾好<br />\n但真係加唔方便"},"citedBy":2,"r